OL,3,CPolice track down sex attacker who
OL,4,Cpreyed on woman after night out
OL,6,FCCTV footage captures Arez Omer
OL,7,Fwalking down the high street in
OL,8,FBrierley Hill after attacking a woman
OL,9,Fon her way home
OL,11,FA man has been jailed after he
OL,12,Ftargeted a woman who was walking home
OL,13,Fafter a night out with friends.
OL,15,FArez Omer, 40, spotted the woman and
OL,16,Fsexually assaulted her as she walked
OL,17,Ffrom Hill Street in Brierley Hill on 8
OL,18,FAugust last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
