PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777539988
OL,3,CPolice track down sex attacker who
OL,4,Cpreyed on woman after night out
OL,6,FThe woman called police and was able
OL,7,Fto give a description of him, which
OL,8,Fwas passed on to CCTV operators at
OL,9,FDudley Council.
OL,11,FCCTV operators then located him and
OL,12,Fguided officers to him - more than two
OL,13,Fmiles away on King Street in Dudley
OL,14,Ftown centre.
OL,16,FDet Sgt Sian Edwards, from West
OL,17,FMidlands Police, said: "This was a
OL,18,Fterrifying attack on a woman simply
OL,19,Fgoing home after a night out with
OL,20,Ffriends in Brierley Hill.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777539988
OL,3,CPolice track down sex attacker who
OL,4,Cpreyed on woman after night out
OL,6,F"Omer has preyed on a woman who
OL,7,Frepeatedly told him to stop and was
OL,8,Fable to fend him off and call the
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,F"There was some excellent teamwork
OL,12,Fbetween call handlers, CCTV operators
OL,13,Fat Dudley Council and Response
OL,14,Fofficers to bring Omer into custody
OL,15,Fquickly enabling us to build a really
OL,16,Fstrong case against him and secure his
OL,17,Fconviction.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777539988
OL,3,CPolice track down sex attacker who
OL,4,Cpreyed on woman after night out
OL,6,F"I'd like to pay tribute to the
OL,7,Fbravery of the woman during and after
OL,8,Fthis awful incident, who we have
OL,9,Fsupported throughout.
OL,11,F"I also hope the prompt actions of our
OL,12,Fofficers in responding to such
OL,13,Fincidents of violence will give
OL,14,Fothers, no matter the circumstances,
OL,15,Fthe courage to come forward. We are
OL,16,Fready to support you and get justice."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
