OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1777539988
OL,3,CPolice track down sex attacker who
OL,4,Cpreyed on woman after night out
OL,6,FCouncillor Phil Atkins, from Dudley
OL,7,FCouncil, said: "I welcome the court
OL,8,Fjudgment following this shocking and
OL,9,Fupsetting case, and our thoughts are
OL,10,Fwith the victim of this abhorrent
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,F"I would like to thank the team, who
OL,14,Fwere able to utilise our CCTV to
OL,15,Flocate footage of the perpetrator
OL,16,Fwithin 90 minutes of the attack and
OL,17,Fsupport police in finding his
OL,18,Flocation."
